description.narrative: Output 1.1 More children, adolescents and their mothers affected by health outbreaks access timely and quality lifesaving health and nutrition interventions, which contributes to Adolescent Health And Nutrition, Child Health, Child Health (Covid), Immunization. UNICEF aims to achieve this through Advocacy And Public Engagement, Fostering Innovation And Use Of New Technologies, Systems Strengthening And Institution Building, United Nations Working Together. This contributes to the following Country Programme result: By 2022, more vulnerable neonates, infants and children survive and thrive and fewer women die during pregnancy and childbirth
